cats SELE type HB2 .and. segid PROA .and. resid 3 .and. (resname SERO .or. resname SERD) END
cats SELE type HB1 .and. segid PROA .and. resid 3 .and. (resname SERO .or. resname SERD) END
cats SELE type HG1 .and. segid PROA .and. resid 3 .and. (resname SERO .or. resname SERD) END
END
